1. *Potrebne* su mi nove cipele. (I need new shoes.)
2. Hrana i voda su *potrebne* za opstanak. (Food and water are necessary for survival.)
3. Da bi se uspešno završio projekat, *potrebne* su nam dodatne resurse. (In order to successfully complete the project, we need additional resources.)
4. *Potrebne* su mi tvoje usluge. (I need your services.)
5. U ovom trenutku, *potrebne* su nam jasne smernice. (At this moment, clear guidelines are necessary.)
6. Kompaniji su *potrebne* nove ideje kako bi se povećao profit. (The company needs new ideas in order to increase profits.)
7. Svi zaposleni moraju da ispune *potrebne* uslove za dobijanje nagrade. (All employees must meet the necessary requirements to receive the award.)
8. Izvršiti određene promene je *potrebno* kako bi se unapredio proces proizvodnje. (Making certain changes is necessary in order to improve the production process.)
9. *Potrebno* je da se prijave do 31. marta. (It is necessary to apply by March 31st.)
10. Bez obzira na teškoće, *potrebno* je nastaviti borbu. (Despite the difficulties, it is necessary to continue the fight.)

Note: The word "potrebne" is an adjective in all of these sentences and agrees with the noun it modifies in gender, number, and case. The form of the word changes based on these factors.